articles.title: HIGH AUTHORITY GUEST POSTING SITES + NICHE GUEST POSTING SERVICE
articles.body:
[HIGH AUTHORITY GUEST POSTING SITES](http://www.guestpostingsites.com/) + NICHE [GUEST POSTING SERVICE](http://www.guestpostingsites.com/)

**Guest Posting Service & Blogger Outreach**

Our guest post outreach service is made on long-term relationships with a large number of site owners. We only use real sites which may have verified organic and natural traffic. Your guest posts are guaranteed, you only pay for links that are published.

**Real Sites with Organic Traffic**

Enjoy peace of mind in your link constructing. All Loganix guest post sites have organic and natural rankings and traffic (predicated on Ahrefs/SEMRush organic and natural traffic estimates) to ensure the sites are trusted by se's. Historic organic and natural traffic numbers are also reviewed by our team to avoid sites that might have been penalized. All the spammy PBNs, stick to real sites with real traffic.

**SELECT THE Sites & Track The Results**

Never worry about being surprised with a bad link. We will choose the most relevant guest post domains for your site and present them for you. Approve the domains we’ve picked or request a replacement, when you’re happy with the site picked we’ll reach work on your post.

All order progress is tracked along the way, letting you see exactly where your guest posts are along the way. Once published you’ll also receive an update from us with the URL to the published post.

*New* (optional) Have we make the picks for you (no pre-approval) and save $10 per guest post.

**Sites We USE & Content**

The guest posting sites we use cover a multitude of topics, we make reference to these kinds of sites as multi-topic. Our writers will craft quite happy with issues that are themed to fit your selected URL, so your desired anchor text can be naturally located in to the article. Have a look at our new Content Upgrade option that will give you a supplementary 250+ words of content as well as the choice to review and suggest edits before your guest post is submitted.

If you’re looking for bigger guest post sites with a tighter topic match to your link/money site, check out our Authority Links product.

**Guaranteed Placement**

Enjoy the peace of mind that is included with a guarantee! If a contributor can’t deliver on the guest post, we’ll find you the same or better link opportunity. Happy customers are our fuel. If you are not pleased with our service or deliverables, trust that you’ve found a team willing bend over backward to do right by you.
